the world was built by dorks.

03:14.736 --> 03:16.863
You think a cool guy
invented Stonehenge?

03:16.905 --> 03:19.908
No way, dork central.
Total virgin stuff.

03:19.949 --> 03:21.493
- Yeah, that's where
I'm gonna agree

03:21.534 --> 03:23.036
